🎬 StreamHub – Ultra-Fast Torrent Video Streaming Application

StreamHub is a high-performance, ad-free, and fully responsive web application that enables users to stream video content directly from magnet links, torrent files, or direct video URLs in real-time, eliminating the need for downloads. Designed for local device use, StreamHub provides a seamless streaming experience powered by decentralized peer-to-peer networks.

Developed using cutting-edge technologies such as WebTorrent, Node.js, and Vite, StreamHub is engineered to deliver a buffer-free experience directly on your local device.

🚀 Key Features

🎥 Instant Torrent Streaming: Users can paste a magnet URI and begin watching immediately on their local devices.

⏩ Custom Video Controls: Features include 10-second forward/backward skip buttons and arrow key support for enhanced navigation.

📂 Automatic File Detection: Automatically selects the appropriate video file from the torrent payload.

📡 Real-time Torrent Statistics: Displays essential information such as download speed, number of peers, and file size.

🌓 Dark Mode User Interface: A minimalistic, modern, and mobile-friendly design.

🌐 CORS-enabled Express API: A secure backend that supports cross-origin requests for local applications.

🔁 Single Page Application (SPA) Friendly Routing: Built with HTML5 history support and fallback routing for improved user experience.

