🔗 API Endpoints

POST /api/start – Initiates torrent streaming using a magnet URI.

GET /api/stream/:infoHash/:fileIndex – Streams video with HTTP Range support.

GET /api/info/:infoHash – Retrieves torrent statistics.

GET /api/torrents – Lists all active torrents.

GET /api/health – Checks the health status of the application.

